329 66 "The Assassins Attack! The Great Battle on Ice Begins!"Transliteration: "Osoi Kuru Shikaku-tachi! Kōri Ue Daibatoru Kaishi" (Japanese:襲い来る刺客たち!氷上大バトル開始) Directed by: Hiroyuki SatōStoryboarded by: Naotoshi Shida Takuya Masumoto November 4, 2007(2007-11-04)[76] January 17, 2016

Using the Shark Submarine, Nami and Franky find out that penguins are moving the icebergs before they are attacked with Usopp and Sanji knocked off theThousand Sunnyinto an ice cavern. Though Nami and Franky evaded the penguins, they are confronted by Hockera  while Usopp and Sanji encounter Arbelle and her husband Salchow. At the same time, as Robin encounters Lil, Luffy and Chopper and the Phoenix Pirates are attacked by Brindo who is after the bounty on both Luffy and Puzzle. Meanwhile, Zoro stumbles upon Lovely Land, the Accino Family's HQ.
